Summary: The Montgomery County Sheriff’s Office is seeking the public’s help in locating Guillermo Fernandez aka Jose Alvarez -Fernandez . Mr. Fernandez is wanted by Detectives with the Montgomery County Sheriff’s Office, for the murder that occurred at 23600 block of Goode Road, Cleveland, Texas on August 3, 2017. Mr. Fernandez is considered armed and dangerous and is a documented MS -13 gang member.
